# ===========================================================================
# documentation-template — .gitignore
# ===========================================================================
# This template is runtime-agnostic: the reference-harvester skill adapts to
# whatever runtime is installed (Python / Node.js / PowerShell / shell), and the
# docs/ folder may hold code samples in any language. The sections below ignore
# the standard build, cache, and binary artifacts those runtimes produce.
# Trim any section you don't need.
# ===========================================================================

# --- Local reference material ----------------------------------------------
# references/ is a LOCAL-ONLY working area (downloaded pages, PDFs, the project
# plan) aggregated for AI context. Never published. Its README.md is the single
# tracked file so the folder survives a clone.
references/*
!references/README.md

# --- Claude Code local-only artifacts --------------------------------------
.claude/*.local.json
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock

# --- Editor / OS clutter ----------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
ehthumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*~
*.tmp
*.bak
.idea/
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
!.vscode/settings.json

# --- Generic compiled / binary artifacts -----------------------------------
*.o
*.obj
*.a
*.lib
*.so
*.so.*
*.dylib
*.dll
*.exe
*.out
*.app
*.class
*.pdb

# --- Archives produced by builds (commit deliberate assets via `git add -f`)-
*.7z
*.gz
*.tar
*.rar
# (.zip is intentionally NOT ignored — docs/ assets are often zipped.)

# --- Python ----------------------------------------------------------------
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.Python
.venv/
venv/
env/
ENV/
*.egg-info/
.eggs/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
pip-log.txt

# --- Node.js / JavaScript / TypeScript -------------------------------------
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
.npm/
.pnpm-store/
.yarn/cache/
*.tsbuildinfo
.eslintcache

# --- .NET / C# --------------------------------------------------------------
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
*.user
*.suo
.vs/

# --- Java / JVM -------------------------------------------------------------
*.jar
*.war
*.ear
target/
.gradle/
build/

# --- Go ---------------------------------------------------------------------
*.test
/vendor/

# --- Rust -------------------------------------------------------------------
/target/
Cargo.lock

# --- PowerShell / Windows scripting ----------------------------------------
*.ps1xml.bak

# --- Logs & coverage --------------------------------------------------------
*.log
logs/
coverage/
.nyc_output/

# --- Environment & secrets --------------------------------------------------
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key

# --- Headless-browser runtime caches (reference-harvester skill) ------------
.harvest-cache/
.playwright/
.cache/
